race.comment: SOUNDS UNUSUAL (8) should get the desired tempo today as he stretches out to this trip for the first time, third-up. Launched late from back in the field when second over 1600m at Randwick. Senior rider goes on and can race closer from the draw. Has solid top-three claims. UNLIMITED (4) talented gelding who had the race parcelled up topping the rise when a decisive 2.5 len winner over 2000m at Randwick. Should cope with the weight rise and expected to go close. ELLIPTICAL (3) set to peak at his fourth run back and meets UNLIMITED better at the weights. Can roll forward with the claim and not to be underestimated. LET'S FLY (9) gets another chance on the limit at the each way price. LENNOX (6) has won out to 2200m and must be kept safe fourth-up.
